{"tid":1466553,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"仇係要報，但要報得啱","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:52:46.000Z","uid":52271,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bf261957786d3c50a60235cd5508ef05414f15c1","tid":1466553,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"好多人以今日阻旅客為例話要攬炒，頭先打個支那仔話要報仇<br />\n我唔講捉唔捉鬼<br />\n我只想講返阻旅客，你塞住佢唔俾佢入閘，我係唔認同嘅。我認為最少要開返條路俾人<br />\n有人話攬炒嘛，但希望大家諗清楚，攬炒係要攬機管局/香港，而唔係攬外國人，咁樣係攬自己炒<br />\n關於頭先個支那仔，作為同路人，梗係明白支那人咁多年黎嘅衰野，大家憎佢都好正常<br />\n但大家要諗下，射爆眼，打手足嘅係香港警察，或者係喬裝成香港警察嘅支那仔。就咁捉住個支那仔黎行私刑，對個運動真係好？<br />\n我唔係要割，但有不同意見，想大家好，都要提出黎大家討論下<br />\n希望大家唔好被仇恨支配"},{"pid":"bf500a2851c972c48e0d81cb1de05861824fb381","tid":1466553,"uid":95487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有<br />\n唔會捉得晒<br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779f8b746d4e17e5b95d95f9da7abb50a8615c98","tid":1466553,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"黑警白衫攻擊時就無差別<br />\n<br />\n我地反擊就下下要對準目標，對家係中共黨媒你都話係𣈴唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你贏比我睇啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ff3e20fa4042cce492c8e1c580e22f34b211f17","tid":1466553,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:32.000Z","msg":"今日一役係不利，甚至係挫折<br />\n希望大家能夠重整旗鼓"},{"pid":"e3bccb2242f453284b13a9f17d33471665c8e7a7","tid":1466553,"uid":55583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"779f8b746d4e17e5b95d95f9da7abb50a8615c98","tid":1466553,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"黑警白衫攻擊時就無差別<br />\n<br />\n我地反擊就下下要對準目標，對家係中共黨媒你都話係𣈴唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你贏比我睇啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:22.000Z","msg":"咁你唔出街見人就打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28696df337c0da67cd0ebb8322f0d3f3a9b44db","tid":1466553,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"779f8b746d4e17e5b95d95f9da7abb50a8615c98","tid":1466553,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"黑警白衫攻擊時就無差別<br />\n<br />\n我地反擊就下下要對準目標，對家係中共黨媒你都話係𣈴唔準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你贏比我睇啦柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"你同我咁講係冇所謂架<br />\n如果你係要我嘅支持<br />\n黑警白衫係有極權支持，你有冇？<br />\n你無極權嘅支撐就想同對家做同樣嘅事，如果你覺得呢樣係你想爭取嘅野，冇計"},{"pid":"4b5c3ad5b72a0c9052bd577dae73190fa527eea1","tid":1466553,"uid":55583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3bccb2242f453284b13a9f17d33471665c8e7a7","tid":1466553,"uid":55583,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"779f8b746d4